.TH "LIGHTNING-PEER-FEE-PPM-AVG" 1 "May 2026" "lightning 0.6.0" "User Commands"
.SH NAME
lightning-peer-fee-ppm-avg \- FEAT-2046 verb
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B lightning peer-fee-ppm-avg
.SH DESCRIPTION
peer-fee-ppm-avg for lightning CLI (FEAT-2046).
.PP
Computes the average fee_per_millionth (ppm) across all peer channels
by querying listpeerchannels.
.PP
Output: JSON from CLN.
.SH EXIT STATUS
.TP
.B 0
Always.
